  "events": [
    {
      "event_id": "70902111_e00001",
      "play_id": "70902111",
      "scene_id": "70902111_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 1,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "杜丽娘上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902111_e00002",
      "play_id": "70902111",
      "scene_id": "70902111_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "懒画眉",
      "speakers": [
        "杜丽娘"
      ],
      "text": "最撩人春色是今年，少甚么低就高来粉画垣。原来春心无处不飞悬。是睡荼蘼抓住裙衩线，恰便是花似人心向好处牵。",
      "text_length": 52
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902111_e00003",
      "play_id": "70902111",
      "scene_id": "70902111_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "春香上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902111_e00004",
      "play_id": "70902111",
      "scene_id": "70902111_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "春香"
      ],
      "text": "方才午膳已过，不知小姐哪里去了，不免寻她则个。呀！",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902111_e00005",
      "play_id": "70902111",
      "scene_id": "70902111_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "惜花赚",
      "speakers": [
        "春香"
      ],
      "text": "何意婵娟，小立在垂垂花树边。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902111_e00006",
      "play_id": "70902111",
      "scene_id": "70902111_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "春香"
      ],
      "text": "小姐吓！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902111_e00007",
      "play_id": "70902111",
      "scene_id": "70902111_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "惜花赚",
      "speakers": [
        "春香"
      ],
      "text": "你才朝膳，个人无伴怎游园？",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902111_e00008",
      "play_id": "70902111",
      "scene_id": "70902111_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杜丽娘"
      ],
      "text": "吖！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902111_e00009",
      "play_id": "70902111",
      "scene_id": "70902111_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "惜花赚",
      "speakers": [
        "杜丽娘"
      ],
      "text": "画廊前，深深蓦见衔泥燕，随步名园是偶然。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902111_e00010",
      "play_id": "70902111",
      "scene_id": "70902111_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "惜花赚",
      "speakers": [
        "春香"
      ],
      "text": "娘回转，幽闺窣地教人见，小庭深院。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902111_e00011",
      "play_id": "70902111",
      "scene_id": "70902111_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杜丽娘"
      ],
      "text": "吖！原来如此，我知道了。你好生答应夫人去，我随后就来。",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902111_e00012",
      "play_id": "70902111",
      "scene_id": "70902111_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "春香"
      ],
      "text": "是。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902111_e00013",
      "play_id": "70902111",
      "scene_id": "70902111_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "春香"
      ],
      "text": "闲花傍砌如依主，娇鸟嫌笼会骂人。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902111_e00014",
      "play_id": "70902111",
      "scene_id": "70902111_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "春香下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902111_e00015",
      "play_id": "70902111",
      "scene_id": "70902111_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杜丽娘"
      ],
      "text": "春香已去，咱好寻梦也。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902111_e00016",
      "play_id": "70902111",
      "scene_id": "70902111_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "忒忒令",
      "speakers": [
        "杜丽娘"
      ],
      "text": "那一答可是湖山石边？这一答是牡丹亭畔。嵌雕栏芍药芽儿浅。一丝丝垂杨线，一丢丢榆荚钱。线儿春甚金钱吊转！",
      "text_length": 51
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902111_e00017",
      "play_id": "70902111",
      "scene_id": "70902111_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杜丽娘"
      ],
      "text": "昨日梦里，那书生将柳枝来赠我，要我题咏，强我欢会之时。好不话长也。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902111_e00018",
      "play_id": "70902111",
      "scene_id": "70902111_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "嘉庆子",
      "speakers": [
        "杜丽娘"
      ],
      "text": "是谁家少俊来近远，敢迤逗这香闺去沁园，话到其间腼腆。他捏这眼奈烦也天，咱噷这口待酬言。",
      "text_length": 43
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902111_e00019",
      "play_id": "70902111",
      "scene_id": "70902111_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "尹令",
      "speakers": [
        "杜丽娘"
      ],
      "text": "咱不是前生爱眷，又素乏平生半面，则道来生出现，乍便今生梦见，生就个书生，恰恰生生抱咱去眠。",
      "text_length": 45
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902111_e00020",
      "play_id": "70902111",
      "scene_id": "70902111_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杜丽娘"
      ],
      "text": "我想那书生这些光景，好不动人春意也！",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902111_e00021",
      "play_id": "70902111",
      "scene_id": "70902111_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "品令",
      "speakers": [
        "杜丽娘"
      ],
      "text": "他倚太湖石，立着咱玉婵娟。待把俺玉山推倒，便日暖玉生烟。捱过雕栏，转过秋千，掯着裙花展，敢席着地怕天瞧见。好一会分明，美满幽香不可言。",
      "text_length": 67
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902111_e00022",
      "play_id": "70902111",
      "scene_id": "70902111_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杜丽娘"
      ],
      "text": "梦到这时节，为甚花片儿掉将下来，把奴惊醒也！",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902111_e00023",
      "play_id": "70902111",
      "scene_id": "70902111_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "豆叶黄",
      "speakers": [
        "杜丽娘"
      ],
      "text": "他兴心儿紧咽咽，呜着咱香肩。俺可也慢掂掂，做意儿周旋。俺可也慢掂掂，做意儿周旋。等闲间，把一个照人儿昏善，这般形现，那般软绵。忑一片撒花心的红影儿吊将来半天。忑一片撒花心的红影儿吊将来半天。敢是咱梦魂儿厮缠？",
      "text_length": 104
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902111_e00024",
      "play_id": "70902111",
      "scene_id": "70902111_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杜丽娘"
      ],
      "text": "寻来寻去，多不见了。那牡丹亭、芍药栏，怎生这般凄凉冷落，杳无人迹？好伤心人也！",
      "text_length": 39
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902111_e00025",
      "play_id": "70902111",
      "scene_id": "70902111_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "玉交枝",
      "speakers": [
        "杜丽娘"
      ],
      "text": "似这等荒凉地面，没多半亭台靠边，敢是咱眯睎色眼寻难见？明放着白日青天，猛教人抓不到魂梦前。霎时间有如活现，打方旋再得俄延，是这答儿压黄金钏匾。",
      "text_length": 71
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902111_e00026",
      "play_id": "70902111",
      "scene_id": "70902111_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杜丽娘"
      ],
      "text": "吓，秀才！秀才！呀啐！我若再见那生呵！",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902111_e00027",
      "play_id": "70902111",
      "scene_id": "70902111_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "三月海棠",
      "speakers": [
        "杜丽娘"
      ],
      "text": "怎赚骗？依稀想像人儿见。那来时荏苒，去也迁延。非远，那雨迹云踪才一转。敢依花傍柳还重现？想昨日今朝眼下心前，阳台一座登时变！（白）再消停一会儿。（望）呀！无人之处，忽然大梅树一株，看梅子累累，可爱人也。（二犯六么令）𠮾，",
      "text_length": 110
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902111_e00028",
      "play_id": "70902111",
      "scene_id": "70902111_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "白",
      "text_length": 1
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902111_e00029",
      "play_id": "70902111",
      "scene_id": "70902111_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "江儿水",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902111_e00030",
      "play_id": "70902111",
      "scene_id": "70902111_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "春香上。春香",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902111_e00031",
      "play_id": "70902111",
      "scene_id": "70902111_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
